## Environment Variables

See `.env.example`.

---

## Postman Collection

Import the `Postman_Collection.json` file into Postman to test all API endpoints.

Authentication flow:

1. Register
2. Login
3. Copy the returned JWT token
4. Add the token as a Bearer Token
5. Test the protected Notes endpoints

